<plot>Taken from the perspective of the imagination of a little boy playing war in the backyard of his home, we see the perspective of the boys imaginations and a reflections of an actual war being played out. The comedy comes from the perception that this is all real, until the war comes to an abrupt end as a result of the interrupting mom, asking for her son to come in for dinner.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?398087</url></doc>
